{"tid":1166494,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周芷若變民國劇女神！祝緒丹5部戲絕美古裝造型還是芷若最仙","createTime":"2019-05-22T12:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T08:08:20.000Z","uid":58335,"like":19,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca9193ac6b2c62563e4b28451ffc4ccc9a34240","tid":1166494,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，佢拍民國劇仲有仙氣仲靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係屌打all女神<br />\n上帝呀，點解你創做左一個咁有仙氣咁靚既祝祝呀??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beauty321.com/albums_photo/11068-20190516122314144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Falbums_photo%2F11068-20190516122314144.jpg&h=19a5b943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.kuyv.cn/201904/18/14-42-42-52-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.kuyv.cn%2F201904%2F18%2F14-42-42-52-10.jpg&h=3fa8a387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日因《倚天屠龍記》周芷若一角人氣暴漲的祝緒丹，在新戲民國劇《一身孤注擲溫柔》的造型再次每出新境界！她和迪麗熱巴都是楊冪公司旗下的新生代小花，不只顏值超高演技也獲得肯定，在《三生三世》飾演的壞心玄女讓人印象深刻，以下這些她出演的古裝角色，你們覺得哪個最美呢~<br />\n<br />\n祝緒丹 飾演《一身孤注擲溫柔》顧婉凝 清新脫俗的民國少女<br />\n《一身孤注擲溫柔》是祝緒丹和阮經天合作的民國劇，去年殺青後祝緒丹也分享了劇中造型，她穿上民國裝同樣超美，讓粉絲更期待她的表演。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beauty321.com/albums_photo/11068-201905161223144003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Falbums_photo%2F11068-201905161223144003.jpg&h=f20d8880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《一身孤注擲溫柔》故事描述軍隊長官與平民女子，在軍閥割據、各方勢力角逐利益的背景下，上演的一段浪漫的生離死別虐戀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beauty321.com/albums_photo/11068-20190516122314902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Falbums_photo%2F11068-20190516122314902.jpg&h=91f1a13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祝緒丹 飾演《倚天屠龍記》周芷若 仙氣爆棚美到令人窒息<br />\n很多影迷都被祝緒丹版的周芷若圈粉，大部分都人都是因《三生三世》的玄女認識她，當時只是個配角，都會劇《一千零一夜》也是替熱巴作配。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beauty321.com/albums_photo/11068-201905161223143734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Falbums_photo%2F11068-201905161223143734.jpg&h=0aa2b3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而《倚天屠龍記》讓她真正走進觀眾視線，把逐漸黑化的周芷若，從純真少女到霸氣外露的掌門人演得非常好，最讓人驚艷的是仙氣爆棚的造型，從任何角度看都美翻天，成為獲得影迷認可的版本，也是粉絲一致認為她最美的古裝角色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beauty321.com/albums_photo/11068-201905161223147892.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Falbums_photo%2F11068-201905161223147892.jpg&h=183118b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祝緒丹 飾演《英雄訣》章犀犀 嬌蠻可愛的蒙古將門之女<br />\n《英雄訣》是2015年拍攝的古裝連續劇，祝緒丹在裡面嘎了一個小角色，是個非常可愛又有點嬌蠻任性的將門之女，她在這部劇的造型一樣很美，因為顏質實在太高了，怎樣都好看。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beauty321.com/albums_photo/11068-201905161223154419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Falbums_photo%2F11068-201905161223154419.jpg&h=e6f86c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.beauty321.com/post/24642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beauty321.com%2Fpost%2F24642&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=8bc5fb49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.beauty321.com/post/24642</a>"},{"pid":"bf88049a5ab8d773e4db80cabf583be332236385","tid":1166494,"uid":134997,"like":5,"dislike":78,"score":-73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0c4HrLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0c4HrLE.jpg&h=9d92da12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-56f96409721e79c186846e1e64533ccb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-56f96409721e79c186846e1e64533ccb&h=fd276951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你班死仔搞到我又J左！<br />\n痴線點忍呀仆街，對奶搖到咁"},{"pid":"e63cac0858321c91c4b5a56a1556ccb8cd56392c","tid":1166494,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-